HEADWORD: Unline
<hw>Un*line"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>line</ets>.]</ety> <def>To take the lining out of;
hence, to empty; <as>as, to <ex>unline</ex> one's purse</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

